  "text": "Using the model, RECON can estimate the energy consumption of any Web page loaded as-is or upon applying any enhancement, without the monitor. It is important to note that RECON's model does not have to be trained on all Web pages or on any enhancements. Since Web page loads exhibit high variance [CITATION_1] , RECON estimates the power consumption for a given instantiation of a Web page load.",
